<SYNC Start=734324><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=734533><P Class=ENCC>
and I cannot feel my legs.
<SYNC Start=737331><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=740840><P Class=ENCC>
- We got a bookcase.<br>
