<SYNC Start=744537><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=745077><P Class=ENCC>
What's this?
<SYNC Start=746442><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=746612><P Class=ENCC>
I would have to say<br>
that is an L-shaped bracket.
<SYNC Start=751675><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=752051><P Class=ENCC>
- Which goes where?<br>
- I have no idea.
<SYNC Start=756147><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=758090><P Class=ENCC>
- Done with the bookcase.<br>
- All finished.
<SYNC Start=761321><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=764563><P Class=ENCC>
This was Carol's favorite beer.
<SYNC Start=767691><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=768634><P Class=ENCC>
She always drank it out of the can.<br>
I should have known.
<SYNC Start=772536><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=775975><P Class=ENCC>
- Start with that, we're out of here.<br>
- Please don't spoil all this fun.
<SYNC Start=781174><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=781380><P Class=ENCC>
Let me ask you.
<SYNC Start=782779><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=782982><P Class=ENCC>
She got the furniture,<br>
the stereo, the good TV.
<SYNC Start=787316><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=787520><P Class=ENCC>
What did you get?
<SYNC Start=789351><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=789555><P Class=ENCC>
