- You got screwed.
<SYNC Start=792649><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=792825><P Class=ENCC>
- Oh, my God.<br>
- I know. I'm such an idiot.
<SYNC Start=797421><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=797630><P Class=ENCC>
I should've known when she went to<br>
the dentist five times a week.
<SYNC Start=802192><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=802401><P Class=ENCC>
I mean, how clean can teeth get?
<SYNC Start=804733><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
