break something valuable of hers.
<SYNC Start=812733><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=812912><P Class=ENCC>
- Say her<br>
- Leg?
<SYNC Start=814539><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=814747><P Class=ENCC>
That's one way of doing it.<br>
I went for the watch.
<SYNC Start=818649><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=819285><P Class=ENCC>
You actually broke her watch?
<SYNC Start=821810><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=822021><P Class=ENCC>
