And I just
<SYNC Start=842236><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=848781><P Class=ENCC>
The machine cut me off again.<br>
Anyway..
<SYNC Start=851807><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=856689><P Class=ENCC>
