It's not me.
<SYNC Start=865592><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=865798><P Class=ENCC>
Not that I have any idea who "me" is<br>
right now, but you just
<SYNC Start=870235><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=872705><P Class=ENCC>
I'm divorced.
