<SYNC Start=887617><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=888621><P Class=ENCC>
We haven't had a relationship<br>
that's lasted longer than a Mento.
<SYNC Start=894856><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=896595><P Class=ENCC>
You have had the love of a woman<br>
for four years.
<SYNC Start=899962><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=900165><P Class=ENCC>
Four years of closeness and sharing,<br>
after which she ripped your heart out.
<SYNC Start=905467><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=905671><P Class=ENCC>
That is why we don't do it!
<SYNC Start=908663><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
