<SYNC Start=991751><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=993425><P Class=ENCC>
What were you going to say?
<SYNC Start=996724><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1000232><P Class=ENCC>
Ever since she left me..
<SYNC Start=1003395><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1003569><P Class=ENCC>
I haven't been able to perform..
<SYNC Start=1006367><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1007072><P Class=ENCC>
sexually.
<SYNC Start=1008903><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1011176><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, God!<br>
I'm so sorry.
<SYNC Start=1014111><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1014279><P Class=ENCC>
Being spit on is probably<br>
