<SYNC Start=1018716><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1020252><P Class=ENCC>
How long?
<SYNC Start=1021719><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1021920><P Class=ENCC>
- Two years.<br>
- Wow.
<SYNC Start=1025014><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1025224><P Class=ENCC>
I'm glad you smashed her watch.
<SYNC Start=1029092><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1029995><P Class=ENCC>
So you still think you might<br>
want that fifth date?
<SYNC Start=1034989><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1036502><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah.<br>
Yeah, I do.
<SYNC Start=1040734><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1041273><P Class=ENCC>
We are gathered here<br>
to join Joanie Louise Cunningham..
<SYNC Start=1046108><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1046311><P Class=ENCC>
and Charles.<br>
Chachi, Chachi, Chachi..
<SYNC Start=1051647><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1052384><P Class=ENCC>
in the bonds of holy matrimony.
