<SYNC Start=1056722><P Class=ENCC>
See!
<SYNC Start=1057780><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1057990><P Class=ENCC>
But Joanie loved Chachi.<br>
That's the difference.
<SYNC Start=1063986><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1064863><P Class=ENCC>
"Grab a spoon."
<SYNC Start=1066694><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1066899><P Class=ENCC>
Do you know how long it's been<br>
since I grabbed a spoon?
<SYNC Start=1070232><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1070569><P Class=ENCC>
Do the words, "Billy, don't be<br>
