Angela has cats.
<SYNC Start=1090286><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1090456><P Class=ENCC>
Right, thanks. It's Julie.<br>
I'm out of here.
<SYNC Start=1095120><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1096695><P Class=ENCC>
Here's the thing. Even if<br>
I could get it together enough..
<SYNC Start=1100995><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1101233><P Class=ENCC>
to ask a woman out..
<SYNC Start=1103827><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
